channel.title: T3CH [Collab?] - For an upcoming event
channel.description:
Ok, so I'm still getting use to the Forum community layout and I'm probably doing this wrong, but as a bit of introduction to myself; I am glad that I can say that I am part of this community and I have been using Auxy for little over 2 years. I grew up listening to Deadmau5 and Pete Tong, and I've always had a knack for music but I couldn't ever put it on paper. Auxy allows me to do so, but I will admit that I am currently stuck on a project, it is for my senior graduation and my song will be played there. I have made the majority of the song but it is just missing a few things and I need a second opinion. I am open to collaborations and what not, but not too sure if you can dm me... still haven't figured that out yet. Anyways, if you have gotten this far, thank you and I look forward to hearing you.
p.s. how do I reply on posts, I dont see the reply button anywhere... thanks
